697
00:46:32,911 --> 00:46:34,393
- Naše!
- Naše!

698
00:46:34,393 --> 00:46:36,929
- Je to naše!
- Ide sa!

699
00:46:37,670 --> 00:46:40,349
Tak fajn. Ideme na to, do toho!

700
00:46:43,387 --> 00:46:45,746
Dajte do toho všetku svoju silu.

701
00:46:45,746 --> 00:46:48,793
Je lepšie umrieť pri behu ako pri práci.

702
00:46:48,793 --> 00:46:50,313
- To viete, však?
- Áno.

703
00:46:50,313 --> 00:46:53,414
- Pripravení?
- Pripravení!

704
00:46:53,414 --> 00:46:54,762
Všetci, do toho!

705
00:47:11,041 --> 00:47:12,309
Šéfe.

706
00:47:13,442 --> 00:47:15,079
- Kŕč!
- Ste v poriadku?

707
00:47:16,110 --> 00:47:18,956
Bežte aj za mňa. No tak!

708
00:47:18,956 --> 00:47:22,032
Choďte, choďte. Bežte!

709
00:47:22,032 --> 00:47:23,465
Prvé miesto musí byť naše!

710
00:47:26,706 --> 00:47:28,043
Pokúsite sa postaviť?

711
00:47:30,782 --> 00:47:31,983
V poriadku?

712
00:47:41,873 --> 00:47:43,045
Woo Jin.

713
00:47:43,697 --> 00:47:46,440
